        Hello! This is a website for Covid-19 plots.
        <br> 
        <br> Website shows two kinds of plots:
        <br> 1. Countries and Cases bar graphs: plot of user-entered country and four other countries from the same continent.
        <br> 2. Spread of Infections in Countries: increase or decrease of infections in three user-entered countries.
        <br> The data source is:
        https://data.europa.eu/euodp/en/data/dataset/covid-19-coronavirus-data
        <br>
        <a href="{{ url_for('country_form') }}">Countries and Cases bar graphs</a>
        <br>
        <a href="{{ url_for('linegraphs_form') }}">Spread of Infections in Countries</a>
        <br>
        <br> Endpoints
        <br> [graph_type]/country
        <br> Returns a dictionary with:
        <br> keys --> user-entered country + 4 other random countries from the same continent as user-entered country
        <br> values --> ”number of cases” for each of the countries 
        <br> [graph_type] is required and should be: bargraph                
        <br> API Version:  1
        <br> Response Format:  json
        <br> Example Resource URL: https://covid-19-visualizations.ey.r.appspot.com/api/v1/bargraph/country?id=India
        <br> Example Response:
        <br> {
              "India": 42.18358533, 
              "Iraq": 83.56697107, 
              "Kuwait": 210.85898832, 
              "Malaysia": 0.56025409, 
              "Palestine": 120.76872829
             }
        <br> Parameters
        <br> Name:  Id
        <br> Description:   Specify a country name as provided in the dropdown list of countries on this site
        <br> Required:  yes
        <br> Default:  none
        <br> 
